description:
Below is an introduction to the roles of the server.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&398987535088615424>
The bottom of the totem pole. However this is nothing to be ashamed of as everyone here has been in your shoes. Treat this as your entrance exam into the Angel Beats! Server and give it all you got!

:small_blue_diamond: <@&398227245669285898>
Congratulations! :confetti_ball: You are now recognized as an active member of our community’s family and have earned your place here.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&399003105305427970>
Amazing! You’re near the top of the food chain. You are now acknowledged as one of the most active members of the community due to your time spent here active and your positive impact on the student body. Thank you for being a model student and someone to look up to. :partying_face:

:small_blue_diamond: <@&533095365973508096>
The staff team of the server. They help enforce the rules, run the server and introduce new guild members around our beloved School, but most importantly they make sure your stay is as pleasant as possible and that homework gets handed in on time.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&497890598267650058>
Hey, it's your birthday! Have a good time and enjoy your day!
title: Roles
